{"tid":300552,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"拒已婚男子表白 鄭州女子遭報復被刺66刀","createTime":"2017-06-28T04:13:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-28T05:06:33.000Z","uid":1393,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0565881c5d8cfe2e1a3abe2f239f340f5c5f70c2","tid":300552,"uid":1393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T04:13:57.000Z","msg":"【星島日報報道】鄭州一名女子因拒絕已婚男子表白，遭報復被刺66刀重傷送院。<br />\n<br />\n28歲的陝西好女子雯雯（化名），在河南鄭州打工，屢遭已婚男子糾纏，多次表白無果後，10日凌晨3時許，男子喪失理智，報復雯雯，連捅了她66刀。救護人員抵達現場發現雯雯渾身是血，倒在鄭州某小區租住的樓層電梯間門口，經初步檢查，女子的胸部、腹部、背部有60多處刀傷，由於失血過多，處於休克狀態。<br />\n<br />\n醫護人員一方面進行搶救，一方面繼續嘗試著聯絡她的家人，送入院後手術一直從早上6時做到下午2時，雯雯轉送到重症監護室進一步接受術後觀察治療。<span style=\"color: red;\">在重症監護室3天後，雯雯的病情逐步平穩，脫離危險期後轉入到胸外科。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%8B%92%E5%B7%B2%E5%A9%9A%E7%94%B7%E5%AD%90%E8%A1%A8%E7%99%BD-%E9%84%AD%E5%B7%9E%E5%A5%B3%E5%AD%90%E9%81%AD%E5%A0%B1%E5%BE%A9%E8%A2%AB%E5%88%BA66%E5%88%80-012800932.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E6%258B%2592%25E5%25B7%25B2%25E5%25A9%259A%25E7%2594%25B7%25E5%25AD%2590%25E8%25A1%25A8%25E7%2599%25BD-%25E9%2584%25AD%25E5%25B7%259E%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E5%25AD%2590%25E9%2581%25AD%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E5%25BE%25A9%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E5%2588%25BA66%25E5%2588%2580-012800932.html&d=u1%2FEs3OS3SrFj2rHSft%2FFTQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=33bdf232\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%8B%92%E5%B7%B2%E5%A9%9A%E7%94%B7%E5%AD%90%E8%A1%A8%E7%99%BD-%E9%84%AD%E5%B7%9E%E5%A5%B3%E5%AD%90%E9%81%AD%E5%A0%B1%E5%BE%A9%E8%A2%AB%E5%88%BA66%E5%88%80-012800932.html</a><br />\n<br />\n強國人生命力真係好強<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db331de1997edc0baeff0192142015ccf701bfef","tid":300552,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T04:18:35.000Z","msg":"又專登唔吉致命位？"},{"pid":"d67574b8a3f299624f7f7231c4c1016c51cb0ed3","tid":300552,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T04:29:27.000Z","msg":"香港紀錄：9刀（女學護）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n中國紀錄：66刀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f58dfaa9041805bb65a1732ba68868876139a60","tid":300552,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T04:36:29.000Z","msg":"66刀都唔死<br />\n唔怪得毛魔殺7千萬人轉眼又多到變13億"},{"pid":"224a2681e49ef28d1f70e7d1e91bb22ca80b6309","tid":300552,"uid":67500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T05:06:33.000Z","msg":"咪撚貼傷口圖，勁撚核突，密集恐懼"}]}